21:34.883 --> 21:36.466
And so we're just going to pick it up.

21:36.642 --> 21:43.210
from the beginning, and as we do, what we're gonna see is David is going to help us see four things about who God is that informs who we are.

21:44.071 --> 21:44.452
Got that?

21:44.492 --> 21:46.735
All right, look at verse one.

21:48.056 --> 21:51.881
He says this, oh Lord, you searched me.

21:52.722 --> 21:53.323
You know me.

21:53.804 --> 21:57.388
You know when I sit down and when I rise up, you discern my thoughts from afar.

21:57.468 --> 21:59.671
You search out my path and my lying down.

21:59.931 --> 22:01.634
You're acquainted with all my ways.

22:02.074 --> 22:05.138
Even before a word is on my tongue, behold,

22:05.346 --> 22:07.228
