24:09.557 --> 24:13.242
It's saying, God calls his shot and he makes it every single time.

24:13.903 --> 24:17.168
Like, he knows exactly what's going to happen.

24:17.549 --> 24:19.652
Not yet what has, but what will.

24:20.894 --> 24:22.356
He knows all that actually exists.

24:22.697 --> 24:23.758
