24:23.798 --> 24:27.764
Second part is that he also knows all that could possibly exist.

24:28.565 --> 24:28.946
Meaning,

24:30.530 --> 24:35.075
He knows completely about what could but won't happen.

24:35.715 --> 24:36.296
Isn't that crazy?

24:37.497 --> 24:40.200
Matthew 11, Jesus says, what are you coursing?

24:40.220 --> 24:41.241
What do you Bethsaida?

24:41.602 --> 24:47.308
For if the mighty works done in you had been done entire inside them, they would have repented long ago in sackcloth and ashes.

24:48.449 --> 24:48.809
