25:46.080 --> 25:51.926
There are animators that have come up with creatures in movies that don't exist in the real world.

25:52.366 --> 25:53.888
But God's like, I knew about that one.

25:54.448 --> 25:56.210
I knew about that one too.

25:56.354 --> 25:58.297
things we've never even thought about.

25:58.597 --> 26:05.426
