26:46.328 --> 26:53.316
It's simple and it's eternal, which just means he's never gonna learn anything that he doesn't already know.

26:54.217 --> 26:55.538
He knows it all right now.

26:55.842 --> 26:58.765
Okay, that's how big God is.

26:59.465 --> 27:04.070
