29:06.979 --> 29:14.048
God knows the words you whisper under your breath so that no one would ever hear them, that he has.

29:14.929 --> 29:21.458
God knows the very thing that you are fully intending to take to the grave with you.

29:23.138 --> 29:25.901
And yet he wants you to know he went to the grave for that thing too.

29:26.902 --> 29:29.986
He knows everything about you.

29:31.187 --> 29:33.389
He knows the answer to that first question.

29:33.429 --> 29:34.270
What's your biggest regret?

29:34.691 --> 29:37.294
He knows it because he was there for it.

29:39.896 --> 29:40.697
