What does that mean?

31:40.274 --> 31:43.538
It means God is present in all places

31:43.650 --> 31:45.652
with every part of his being.

31:46.373 --> 31:51.398
He is present in all places, which means you should never play hide and seek with the big guy.

31:51.418 --> 31:53.521
Like you're not gonna go somewhere where he doesn't know where you're at.

31:53.541 --> 31:55.182
He's already there right now.

31:55.222 --> 31:56.644
That's what Jeremiah 23 says.

31:57.064 --> 32:00.508
It says, am I a God at hand declares the Lord and not a God far away?

32:01.269 --> 32:04.112
Can man hide himself in secret places so that I cannot see him?

32:05.433 --> 32:09.778
