He says, if I ascend to the heights of heaven, meaning if I go to the land of the living, if I descend to the depths of shield, that place of the dead, God, you're there.

32:33.437 --> 32:37.944
He says, if I rise up on the wings of the morning, the dawn, where's the sunrise?

32:38.585 --> 32:39.346
In what direction?

32:40.482 --> 32:52.538
In the east, meaning if you go as far east as possible, or if I go to the uttermost parts of the sea, which from David's vantage point in Israel would be which direction?

32:53.420 --> 32:53.820
West.

32:55.302 --> 32:59.768
No matter how far east I go, no matter how far west I go, you're there too.

