34:16.903 --> 34:34.002
I've had some stunning encounters, some powerful moments with God in awesome places, like at the summit of a 14er or in the Christian catacombs of Rome or singing amongst thousands of believers, young adults, just like myself in this room here tonight.

34:35.362 --> 34:43.631
And yet some of the most powerful moments with God have not been in the most stunning of places, but in the most simple.

34:44.573 --> 34:47.756
