Sin is a deliberate movement away from the presence of God.

36:16.716 --> 36:20.060
For others of us, we moved unwillingly from his presence.

36:20.100 --> 36:22.323
That's what suffering can do in the life of a person.

36:22.643 --> 36:28.050
