37:03.215 --> 37:07.121
Because when you were at your furthest, Christ came for you.

37:07.843 --> 37:13.992
And if you're here tonight and you're resonating with this idea that, man, God, I just want to be near you again.

37:14.012 --> 37:15.354
I promise you.

37:15.515 --> 37:16.496
I promise you.

37:16.897 --> 37:18.219
He wants to be near you too.

37:18.279 --> 37:20.182
He's with you right now.

37:20.222 --> 37:22.105
And He's come for you tonight.

37:23.046 --> 37:25.330
You need only place your faith in Him.

37:27.650 --> 37:29.131
